decks.notes: The focus of this deck is to control the game by using powerful Planeswalkers like Dack Fayden, Narset, and Oko to generate card advantage and disrupt the opponent's strategy. The deck also includes versatile counter spells like Force of Will and Flusterstorm, along with efficient removal like Lightning Bolt and Wrenn and Six. By utilizing disruptive creatures like Collector Ouphe and Ragavan, as well as card filtering effects like Expressive Iteration, the deck aims to outvalue the opponent while maintaining control of the game through its powerful spells and proactive threats.
